  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Hops and hops products marketing standards after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Marketing standards for hops producers, manufacturers, retailers and distributors after Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

